articles.title: Declan Rice: Everyone that voted for Arsenal midfielder to win The Best FIFA Men's Player 2023 - 90min UK
articles.description: Declan Rice finished 12th in The Best FIFA Men's Player standings for 2023 - this is everyone who voted for him.
articles.content:
